 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">The right decoration for K500 and the rest of the Port Authority line.</p>
 </a>
 <a href="/company-stores/" class="group border border-hairline bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gold-500">
 <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal group-hover:text-gold-600">Sales Team Company Stores</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">Stocked Port Authority polos with your logo on file. Reps order on demand.</p>
 </a>
 <a href="/blog/logo-digitizing-101-embroidery/" class="group border border-hairline bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gold-500">
 <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal group-hover:text-gold-600">Logo Digitizing 101</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">How a clean digitized file makes Port Authority polo embroidery look sharp.</p>
 </a>
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>

 <!-- CTA — full-bleed photographic dark band -->
 <section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-navy-950">
 <img src="/images/generated/cta-bluehour.jpg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
 <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-navy-950/80"></div>
 <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-20 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
 <h2 class="mb-4 font-heading text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Quote on custom Port Authority <span class="text-gold-400">fast.</span></h2>
 <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-navy-200">Stocked K500s ship in a week. Talk to a real human.</p>
 <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
 <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary text-base">Get a Free Quote</a>
 <a href="tel:+17029048923" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-2 py-3 font-mono text-base font-medium tracking-wide text-white transition-colors hover:text-gold-400">702.904.8923</a>
 </div>
